text: Chanteloup may refer to several communes in France: *Chanteloup, Eure, in the Eure département *Chanteloup, Ille-et-Vilaine, in the Ille-et-Vilaine département *Chanteloup, Manche, in the Manche département *Chanteloup, Deux- Sèvres, in the Deux-Sèvres département *Chanteloup-en-Brie, in the Seine-et- Marne département *Chanteloup-les-Bois, in the Maine-et-Loire département *Chanteloup-les-Vignes, in the Yvelines département It may also refer to: * Château de Chanteloup, a former château in the Indre-et-Loire département
title: Chanteloup
